 <title>Processo:  Change Base Language</title> 
 <para><emphasis> Descrição: </emphasis>Change Base Language</para><para><emphasis> Comentário/Ajuda: </emphasis>In order to enable en_US as a translation you can enable any other language as base language.
If you don't want to have a base language choose a language that won't be used for login.
If all languages are going to be used as login, create a xx_XX language not login and use it as base.</para>
